title: Ep. 711 Are Conservatives Gaining Ground in the Culture Wars?
description:
Summary:
In this episode I address the real-world ramifications of liberal economic policies and provide evidence that the consequences are becoming visible. I also address the FBI’s continued efforts to delay the release of critical information that could entirely dismantle the Russian collusion narrative. 
 
News Picks:
Why did the Mueller team leak their questions for Trump?
 
What is the FBI hiding from us regarding its communications with Crowdstrike?
 
Hyperinflation is destroying the Venezuelan economy. 
 
Liberalism is decimating San Francisco.
 
The Israelis pulled off one of the boldest spy operations I’ve ever heard of. 
 
Another celebrity questions where his tax money is going. 
 
China’s missile development is creating access problems for us.
